                <note rend="inline" type="source">800.51 W 89 Italy/48: Telegram</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The <gloss type="from">Acting Secretary of State</gloss> to
                        the Ambassador in Italy</hi> (<persName type="to">
                        <hi rend="italic">Fletcher</hi>
                    </persName>)</head>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#center">[Paraphrase]</seg>
                </opener>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Washington</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1925-09-01T16:00:00-04:00">
                            <hi rend="italic">September 1, 1925—4 p.m.</hi>
                        </date>
                    </dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>106. Your telegram 132, August 31, 4 p.m. The State Department has informed the
                    bankers that it would not view this financing favorably at the present time.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Grew</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
